{"tid":2185324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"禿鷹：《基本法》無提及香港有三權分立","createTime":"2020-09-02T07:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T13:47:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7a476377bf85fcb94d2e802974fc99129aa43ded","tid":2185324,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"全國政協委員、警務處前處長曾偉雄指，《基本法》沒有提及香港有三權分立，他留意到有人士提出不同意見，但就沒有講明以《基本法》哪一項條文作根據；以他理解，《基本法》寫明特首既是特區政府之首，也是特區之首，最終負有雙重責任，反問若特首只管某些範疇，如何負最終責任。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2355372&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXP%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=1f227e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355372</a>"},{"pid":"a8dcceae8314dcb1b6f2473bf923ff3b6bc04b71","tid":2185324,"uid":346260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"},{"pid":"1a789fcf0b6a644294e7e7f3658fadddfe1dfa59","tid":2185324,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"十二位手足被扣押第九日 務必繼續關注聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184284</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae0b773ddca4cda64ca48ca46287e738f7188d6e","tid":2185324,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T